text: Reisbach may refer to: * Reisbach (Saar), a small town in Saarland, Germany * Reisbach (Vils), a city in Bavaria, Germany in the district of Dingolfing- Landau * Reisbach (Palatinate), a river of Alsace, France, and Rhineland- Palatinate, Germany * Wolfsindis of Reisbach, regional saint of the Middle Ages in Bavaria == See also == * Schachten (disambiguation)
title: Reisbach
